{"tid":2033336,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[鬥黃] 籲民進黨具體修法 國民黨主席江啟臣：別讓「撐香港」淪口號","createTime":"2020-05-24T14:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T15:11:26.000Z","uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85aef668fe4994859ee63370c1c7fd3ef0059523","tid":2033336,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"籲民進黨具體修法 國民黨主席江啟臣：別讓「撐香港」淪口號<br />\n<br />\n2020-05-24 22:07:17<br />\n〔記者林良昇／台北報導〕對於香港民眾今上街反對「港版國安法」，國民黨主席江啟臣表示，中共如果不思如何強化溝通，尋求港人認同，強推「港版國安法」，恐怕反成中共當局的國安破口。也期待民進黨政府具體提出修法行動支持香港，別讓「撐香港」淪為口惠不實的口號。<br />\n<br />\n江啟臣在臉書發文表示，「香港的本色是自由」，他這一代台灣人，曾在戒嚴年代追過港版武俠與港星港片，嚮往過香港作為國際大都會的璀璨視野；長久以來，香港的本色是「自由」。<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3176117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3176117&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMpdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=4459123a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3176117&h=57336c77\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3176117</a><br />\n<br />\nFb貼文: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/191690867518507/posts/3146171818737049/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F191690867518507%2Fposts%2F3146171818737049%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMpdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=eb7d79ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/191690867518507/posts/3146171818737049/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"5a40bf4fd7b1ceb82618833bf9a3f689c7367007","tid":2033336,"uid":83228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"在野國民黨 扮乜"},{"pid":"deac9aaa9fcd9d3993956d9ec17fa019bf734bfd","tid":2033336,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"中華民國收返香港"}]}